<paragraph blockId="347.[151,1437,1297,1647]" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[268,517,1513,1540]" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" pagination="193 - 231" refId="ref369428" refString="Rondani, C. (1865 c) Diptera italica non vel minus cognita descripta vel annotata observationibus nonnullis additis. Fasc. II. Muscidae. Atti della Societa Italiana di Scienze Naturali, 8, 193 - 231." type="journal article" year="1865">Rondani (1865c: 203)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName box="[641,831,1513,1539]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Platychyra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fortis">
<emphasis box="[641,831,1513,1539]" italics="true" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">Platychyra fortis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from just the male sex, without specifying either the 
<taxonomicName box="[199,285,1549,1575]" family="Number" pageId="347" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
or the length of the specimens. We found 
<specimenCount box="[751,885,1550,1576]" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" type="generic" typeStatus="syntype">one syntype</specimenCount>
in this study. This nominal species was described under the generic name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1859" box="[464,587,1585,1611]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Platychyra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[464,587,1585,1611]" italics="true" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">Platychyra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which is an “unjustified emendation of 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1856" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1856" box="[1036,1326,1585,1612]" genus="Platychira" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1036,1154,1585,1611]" italics="true" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">Platychira</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[1161,1326,1585,1612]" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" refId="ref368338" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 226 pp. + [2] pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1856">Rondani, 1856</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
” (
<bibRefCitation author="O'Hara, J. E. &amp; Cerretti, P. &amp; Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L." pageId="347" pageNumber="348" pagination="1 - 268" refId="ref361577" refString="O'Hara, J. E., Cerretti, P., Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L. (2011) Nomenclatural studies toward a world list of Diptera genus-group names. Part II: Camillo Rondani. Zootaxa, 3141, 1 - 268. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3141.1.1" type="journal article" year="2011">
O’Hara 
<emphasis box="[199,255,1621,1647]" italics="true" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">et al.</emphasis>
2011: 147
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
